<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-12-17T09:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-12-17T09:00:00-05:00" n="136" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d136">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 European War 1939/1222:
                            Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-12-17T11:00:00-03:00">December
                                    17, 1939—11 a.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received December 17—10:43 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>439. Department’s 237, December 16, 2 p.m. Cantilo is urgently requesting
                            Aranha’s support for his draft of protest to be made in connection with
                            Declaration of Panama. Aranha says in his opinion Cantilo’s note is
                            satisfactory but of course he wants to cooperate with us. Aranha is
                            talking to President Vargas<note n="30" xml:id="d136fn30">Getulio
                                Vargas, President of Brazil.</note> on whole subject early this
                            afternoon and will talk to me again later.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>